---
title: Pork and Chinese Eggplant Stir-Fry with Garlic Soy Sauce and Brown Rice
description: Chinese eggplant, longer and thinner-skinned than its Italian cousin, is perfect for stir-frying. Sautéed with summer squash, pork, and an umami-packed sauce, this stir-fry hits all the marks. Brown rice is a healthy swap we prefer here for its heartiness.
